Sentencas: This paper uses finite element method to study the effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stresses in the bonded compliant seal (BCS) design of a planar solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The effects of Al2O3 thickness, operating temperature, window frame thickness, foil thickness and cell length on thermal stresses have been discussed.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results show that compressive stresses are generated in Al2O3 film.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A bowing deformation is generated due to the BCS design, which can trap and relax some thermal stresses.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: With Al2O3 thickness increase, compressive stresses in Al2O3 film and foil are decreased slightly, while tensile stresses in BNi2 and frame are increased.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: With operating temperature increase, compressive stress in Al2O3 is increased greatly, while the stresses in foil.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The bowing deformation is increased with operating temperature increase.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The window frame thickness has little effect on thermal stresses and bowing deformation.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: With sealing foil thickness increase, thermal stresses and bowing deformation are increased.
Titulo: Effect of Al2O3 film on thermal stress in the bonded compliant seal design of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The cell length has little effect on thermal stresses, but reducing the cell length can decrease the bowing deformation.
